-- German Life Insurers Face Complaint Over Advice, Bild Reports
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2011-12-20T07:11:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-20/german-life-insurers-face-complaint-over-advice-bild-reports.html
About 280 customers have filed a
complaint against 11 German life insurers, seeking 2 million
euros ($2.6 million) for allegedly inadequate advice,  Bild
Zeitung  reported today, without saying where it got the
information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
